                  </hi>. I know the prisoner to be the man who came to hire the truck.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I never was at his place at all. <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi>. I have no doubt of him—he came to me previous to having it from my daughter, and said he wanted it—I had some knowledge of him before, as he had been twice before, and left me one of Mr. Fisher's cards.</p>
